I've been going to this Macaroni Grille location for many years and it seems that over time it just keeps getting worse.  They are constantly out of signature items and the service has been dismal of late.  Most of servers are nice and friendly but they are constantly understaffed.  It seems as if the managers like to have as few staff as necessary on hand, so when it gets busy, the customers suffer.  I will look for better options in the west valley if they don't change this practice SOON!  If it wasn't for the delicious Penne Rustica, I would have probably stopped going already.

