Great burgers and atmosphere at The Grind.  The burgers are HUGE and amazing...my personal favorite is the peppercorn.  Combined with some regular or sweet potato fries, it's a great meal. Service always seems to be friendly and prompt. They play music which I enjoy and have a number of TV's above the bar.

